plore ancient temples littered with traps and puzzles. Discover new secrets in an ever-changing environment where Egyptian architecture meets futuristic technology.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326800/extras/3e0709485fce7067aa56752d9e386841.poster.avif?t=1710026174\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326800/extras/3e0709485fce7067aa56752d9e386841.webm?t=1710026174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326800/extras/3e0709485fce7067aa56752d9e386841.mp4?t=1710026174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
